        <h2 class="title-effect">About Company</h2>
        <p>Living Without Borders is a dynamic, Innovative, experienced and dedicated multi level marketing company that is passionate about training people on area of leadership,entrepreneurship and business. Members will equally have opportunities to travel outside the country for the purpose of being trained in this areas.</p>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
       <div class="section-title">
        <h2 class="title-effect">Our Services</h2>
        <p>Our company is service oriented. Our area of specialty is in the human capacity development. To achieve this, we are partnering with professional trainers locally and internationally, and reputable companies to ensure that our partners are trained by the best of hands and companies.</p>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 xs-mb-40">
       <div class="feature-box h-100 active">
        <div class="feature-box-content"><i class="fa fa-paint-brush blue"></i>
         <h4>Leadership Training</h4>
         <p>Everything rises and falls on leadership. Therefore to be successful in life, you must first see yourself as a leader and as well act as one</p>
        </div> <a href="#"></a>
        <div class="feature-box-img" style="background-image: url('/front/images/about/01.jpg');"></div>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 xs-mb-40">
       <div class="feature-box h-100 active">
        <div class="feature-box-content"><i class="fa fa-arrows"></i>
         <h4>Entrepreneurship</h4>
         <p>We believe that every individual irrespective of your profession should be trained in one skill or the other as that is the way forward for our society. We are partnering with reputable companies as well as small scale industries to ensure you are properly skilled.</p>
        </div> <a href="#"></a>
        <div class="feature-box-img" style="background-image: url('/front/images/about/02.jpg');"></div>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
       <div class="feature-box h-100 active">
        <div class="feature-box-content"><i class="fa fa-heart"></i>
         <h4>Business Trainings</h4>
         <p>These trainings will help you achieve your dream as an entrepreneur and an employer of Labour. Giving you a road map to follow when building your own small scale industry and gradually growing it to a very big company</p>
        </div> <a href="#"></a>
        <div class="feature-box-img" style="background-image: url('/front/images/about/03.jpg');"></div>
       </div>
      </div>
